page.title: 11SAMANTHA'S HOME, WECOCK.
page.content: My home in{Robin Gardens}is made of bricks and plaster board. I live in a house and it has stone-cladding and it is semi-detached, it is about 10 years old. My house has not got double glazing and it has a beige door and a front garden and a back garden.The hall is artexed and we have a kitchen, living room, toilet downstairs and a bathroom upstairs. We do not have a separate dining room so we eat in the kitchen. The toilet downstairs is brown and there are three bedrooms and one bathroom upstairs. My bedroom is pink and has Wham Posters everywhere. My brother's bedroom is blue and my mum's is grey. My garden is little but has a patio and a wall.We have a shed and flowers everywhere.We have a barbecue on the grass,we have no trees but are surrounded by a high fence.We do not have a garage or greenhouse.
